<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="/files/documents/Remote%20Learning%20Update%20(4.16.2020)%20(1).pdf" target="_blank">Superintendent's Letter (April 16, 2020) click here. </a></h2>

<hr>
<h3 class="h2" style="text-align: center;"><em>Food Service Program Donations</em></h3>

<h4 style="text-align: center;">School Administrative Unit (SAU) 21 understands that food security is an essential component of student learning. As such, during this remote instruction environment, we continue to provide nutritious meals for all our students, while our physical buildings are closed. Our incredible School Nutrition team is preparing bag breakfasts and lunches equivalent of seven (7) days a week, to any student free of charge during this unprecedented pandemic.   </h4>

<h4 style="text-align: center;">If you are interested in donating to support the SAU 21 Food Service Program, please click the following link:  <a href="http://gf.me/u/xyk2st">gf.me/u/xyk2st</a>
</h4>

<p> </p>

